task.summary: Removed Plane, since there already exists a Plane data structure.
Migrated some MathUtil functionality to Vector, deprecated some code in algebra package, and modified getCol in Mat3f to accept Vector instead of Vec3f.
Added get and set methods to Vector. They are used in Mat4f.
Migrated Functions and SpanCalculator from Rings to Common.
Some improvements to Line and Mat2f. Line has been moved to the space package.
Improved PlaneUV so that intersection accepts a Ray rather than two Vectors.
Mat4f stores double precision values now.
Migrating Rotf to double precision and use of the Vector class instead of Vec3f.
Removed Vec3f. Added operations to Pair.
Added toPair method to Veci. Vec3d implements Triple.
Migrating FloatingPointList so that it uses Scalar.
Migrated StackList, VectorStackList, and Vector4StackList to Common.
Migrated ArrayPool, BulletStack, MatrixStackList, QuatStackList, Transform, and TransformStackList to Common.
Migrated JacobianEntry to Common. Added generics to Resource.
Added toArray method to RGBA. Added constructor for UnicodeResource that accepts a File.
Working towards code generation support. Renamed Graph to Chart to avoid confusion with org.almostrealism.graph.Graph.
Some improvements to the code generation features.
Improved merge in Shell to avoid unmodifiable list.
Introduced AcceleratedFunctions and GPUOperator, as well as some other classes involved in maintaining a OpenCL program and the corresponding set of named functions therein.
Introduced Pipeline (combination of Juncture and Producer). Updated GraphicsConverter so that each column can optionally notify a Pipeline.
Improved RealizableImage so that evaluate returns rapidly with partial image data if the image pixel futures are not complete.
Added isComplete and getCompleted methods to RealizableImage.
Fixed a(n unbelievably challenging to diagnose) problem with hardware acceleration. Introduced hardware acceleration for TransformMatrix.
Store Ray in cl_mem. This is version 0.7.
